explosive bomb, LED bulb, Small led light,  &lt;br&gt;
Halogen bulb in the street, Hot black color plate  &lt;br&gt;
which cannot be seen as hot,  &lt;br&gt;
hot coffee, a cube of ice, and a mountain of snow.Every energy body around us has  &lt;br&gt;
their relevance and purpose,  &lt;br&gt;
